SP Setia Says PNB Buyout Bid Undervalues Stock; Seeks New Offer

-- B y   C h a n   T i e n   H i n
-- 
2011-09-28T23:50:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/sp-setia-says-pnb-buyout-bid-undervalues-stock-seeks-new-offer.html
SP Setia Bhd. (SPSB) ,  Malaysia ’s biggest
listed developer by sales, said Permodalan Nasional Bhd.’s
takeover offer of 3.90 ringgit a share “fundamentally
undervalues” the company and will seek competing offers.  SP Setia will also ask Permodalan, or PNB whether it’s
interested in raising its offer, it said in a statement late
yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chan Tien Hin at 
 thchan@bloomberg.net  